    <i class="far fa-comment-alt"></i>
    <div>댓글 1개</div>
  </div>
  <div class="response__box">
    <i class="far fa-share-square"></i>
    <div>공유 1회</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="contain__reply">
  <div class="reply__profilepic"></div>
  <div class="reply__content">
    <div class="reply__nickname">
      이해쥬
    </div>
    <div class="reply__comment">
      꼽창 선임 재윤아 잘가~
